The night before the big dayAs night closed in, Mr Kim made a tour of some city sights.
Mr Kim and Mr Trump are staying in separate hotels, not far from each other.
'Supremely confident'Mr Balakrishnan, who met Mr Trump and Mr Kim separately on Sunday evening, told the BBC that both leaders were feeling "supremely confident".
It started with significant diplomatic overtures from North Korea towards South Korea during the Winter Olympics.
In March, Mr Trump shocked the world by accepting an invitation from Mr Kim to meet in person.